OL,3,C'Hallmarks of organised crime':
OL,4,CMourners targeted by 'sickening'
OL,5,Clivestream scam
OL,7,FOne woman said it made her feel "sick
OL,8,Fto the stomach" that Facebook had
OL,9,Frefused to remove the scam profile, as
OL,10,FITV News Digital Reporter George
OL,11,FHancorn reports
OL,13,FWhen Phil Humm went to his mum's wake,
OL,14,Fhe was looking forward to celebrating
OL,15,Fher life. What he didn't expect was to
OL,16,Ffind out her ceremony had been
OL,17,Ftargeted by scammers.
OL,19,F"It's sickening to know people are
OL,20,Ftrying to profit from other people's
OL,21,Fgrief," he told us.
