OL,7,F"Especially when you're trying to bury
OL,8,Fyour loved ones."
OL,10,FBefore she died, Pauline had told Phil
OL,11,Fshe wanted people to enjoy the wake,
OL,12,Fdescribing it as "the party
OL,13,Fafterwards".
OL,15,FBut during the celebration, Phil found
OL,16,Fout his cousin had tried to enter bank
OL,17,Fdetails to watch the funeral on a
OL,18,Flivestream - except there was no
OL,19,Fstream of Pauline's ceremony.
