OL,7,FPhil Humm told ITV News finding out
OL,8,Fabout the scam was "distressing"
OL,10,FScammers had taken photos of her and
OL,11,Fdetails of the funeral, using them to
OL,12,Fcreate a Facebook profile with a fake
OL,13,Flivestream link. The link led on to a
OL,14,Fpaywall, demanding money to watch a
OL,15,Fnon-existent stream.
OL,17,FITV News has found hundreds of these
OL,18,Fscam profiles created on Facebook.
