OL,7,FHours before a funeral is due to take
OL,8,Fplace, the scammers bombard relatives
OL,9,Fand friends of the bereaved family
OL,10,Fwith friend requests, hoping they'll
OL,11,Fbelieve it's real - and enter card
OL,12,Fdetails in a panic.
OL,14,FHigh-profile deaths have also been
OL,15,Fstruck by this kind of scam, with
OL,16,Fpolice issuing warnings around the
OL,17,Ffunerals of Southport victim Bebe
OL,18,FKing, and Poppy Atkinson, who died
OL,19,Fafter being struck by a car in Cumbria.
