OL,7,FThe funeral of Dan Turpin's father was
OL,8,Falso impacted. One of his friends
OL,9,Fended up entering her card details on
OL,10,Fthe link, losing around #7 to
OL,11,Ffraudsters - who charge small amounts
OL,12,Fin the hopes of maximising the number
OL,13,Fof people impacted.
OL,15,FDan said she was caught off guard, not
OL,16,Fwanting to disturb him while he was
OL,17,Fmourning to check if it was real.
