OL,7,F"If they were one of my friends, would
OL,8,Fthey come to me on the day of my dad's
OL,9,Ffuneral and question the genuine
OL,10,Freasons of me sending something like
OL,11,Fthat?" he said.
OL,13,F"It's very easy and very smart for
OL,14,Fthem to do that. To catch people in a
OL,15,Fvery vulnerable state. It's disgusting
OL,16,Freally."
OL,18,FDan said the scammers began targeting
OL,19,Fhis friends just an hour before the
OL,20,Ffuneral
