OL,7,FWe also met with Lynne Rawlins, whose
OL,8,Fhusband John's funeral was targeted.
OL,9,FThe family scrambled to warn relatives
OL,10,Fon Facebook, after discovering the
OL,11,Fscam link an hour before his funeral.
OL,13,FShe said: "The day is hard enough as
OL,14,Fit is. Families are struggling,
OL,15,Fthey're suffering, emotionally
OL,16,Feveryone's broken.
OL,18,F"And to have somebody come along and
OL,19,Ftry to scam as many people as they
OL,20,Fcan, I think they're the scum of the
OL,21,Fearth to be honest."
