OL,7,FTrading standards experts have warned
OL,8,Fthe problem has been worsening since
OL,9,Fthe pandemic, where streaming funerals
OL,10,Fgrew in popularity amid strict
OL,11,Flockdown rules.
OL,13,FKatherine Hart, a lead officer at the
OL,14,FChartered Trading Standards Institute,
OL,15,Ftold ITV News: "We have seen a rise in
OL,16,Fthese sorts of scams over the last
OL,17,Ffour years.
OL,19,F"To me, this has all the hallmarks of
OL,20,Fa serious organised crime group."
