OL,7,FITV News asked cybersecurity experts
OL,8,FMalwareBytes to investigate some of
OL,9,Fthe scam profiles.
OL,11,FAnna Brading, Editor in Chief of
OL,12,FMalwareBytes Labs, told us the risk of
OL,13,Fthese scams goes beyond money being
OL,14,Ftaken - with card details likely being
OL,15,Ftraded on the dark web.
OL,17,FShe warned a recent feature released
OL,18,Fby Facebook might be making it easier
OL,19,Ffor funeral scammers to take advantage
OL,20,Fof people.
