OL,7,FIn September 2023, Meta announced it
OL,8,Fwas making it possible to have
OL,9,Fmultiple "personal profiles" under one
OL,10,Faccount on Facebook.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FOnce they've created their main
OL,18,Faccount, a user can then create up to
OL,19,Ffour additional profiles linked to
OL,20,Fthis account.
