OL,7,FMeta said it is possible to "choose
OL,8,Fany name for your additional
OL,9,Fprofiles", but the main profile must
OL,10,Fhave the name someone goes by in
OL,11,Feveryday life.
OL,13,F"Facebook does do verification on
OL,14,Fpeople when you add a profile," Anna
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,F"But this is obviously a new thing on
OL,18,FFacebook where you can just add a
OL,19,Fusername - great for people who want
OL,20,Fto stay private, also great for
OL,21,Fscammers."
