OL,7,FShe told us some of the domains have
OL,8,Fbeen traced to Bangladesh, but it is
OL,9,Foften difficult to track exactly where
OL,10,Fscammers are operating from.
OL,12,FDan and Lynne reported the scams to
OL,13,FFacebook, but the platform told them
OL,14,Fthe profiles wouldn't be taken down,
OL,15,Fas they didn't violate the platform's
OL,16,Fcommunity guidelines.
OL,18,F"It makes me feel sick to the stomach
OL,19,Fthat Facebook aren't helping people,"
