OL,7,FHow do you know if a livestream is
OL,8,Fgenuine?
OL,10,FDarryl Smith, acting president of the
OL,11,FNational Association of Funeral
OL,12,FDirectors (NAFD) said the
OL,13,Fproliferation of livestream scams was
OL,14,Fa "sad state of affairs" - but said
OL,15,Fcommunication with undertakers can
OL,16,Fminimise opportunities for scammers to
OL,17,Fstrike.
OL,19,F"It's about speaking to your funeral
OL,20,Fdirector," he said.
